<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.3.9">
<l>valattaṉaṉ ṟiripura merittava ṉiṭampeṟat tuntit</l>
<l>talatteḻu ticaimukaṉ paṭaittanal lulakamun tāṉum</l>
<l>pulappaṭa piṉṉuntaṉ ṉulakatti lakattaṉaṉ tāṉē</l>
<l>colappuki livaipiṉṉum vayiṟṟuḷa vivaiyavaṉ ṟuyakkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>On [his] right [is] the one who burned the three cities. While the good world, which the one</l>
<l>with a face in [every] direction created in seven areas, and he obtain place in [his] navel,</l>
<l>he himself is moreover inside his world, for the senses to perceive.</l>
<l>When one enters speaking about these, moreover these that are in [his] belly [are] his bond/distraction(?).</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
